==Overview== Operation: Thunder is a [[Platforms/Pinball|pinball machine]] developed and manufactured by [[Companies/Gottlieb|Gottlieb]] in 1992. Operation: Thunder is the last pinball machine made by Gottlieb to use an alphanumeric display. All of the Gottlieb machines produced after Operation: Thunder used a dot-matrix display instead.

